data.description: Make this beauty yours today! 3bedroom, 2bath, 2 car garage and office. This is located in Frenship District, NW Lubbock, 6 minutes away from LCU and 13 minutes from TTU. Very spacious with Open concept, high ceilings and walk-in closets in every room. Two storage sheds in backyard and side of the house. A super nice custom-made pergola in backyard. HVAC replaced in July, stainless steel microwave replaced in September. You must see! Sellers offering $3,000 closing cost assistance!  Priced right to sell!
